name: Pinq\Queryable
short_desc: The standard queryable class, fully implements the queryable API

AsArray.name: AsArray
AsArray.short_desc: Returns the values as an array

AsTraversable.name: AsTraversable
AsTraversable.short_desc: Returns the values as a traversable.
AsTraversable.long_desc:
If the implementation is queryable the following operations will
be performed in memory.

AsCollection.name: AsCollection
AsCollection.short_desc: Returns the values as a collection.
AsCollection.long_desc:
If the implementation is queryable the following operations will
be performed in memory.

AsQueryable.name: AsQueryable
AsQueryable.short_desc: Returns the values as a queryable.

AsRepository.name: AsRepository
AsRepository.short_desc: Returns the values as a repository.

GetProvider.name: GetProvider
GetProvider.short_desc: The query provider for the implementation.

Select.name: Select
Select.short_desc: Returns the values mapped by the supplied function.

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function returning the data to select

SelectMany.name: SelectMany
SelectMany.short_desc: Returns the values mapped by the supplied function and then flattens  the values into a single traversable.

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function returning the data to select

IndexBy.name: IndexBy
IndexBy.short_desc: Index the values according to the supplied mapping function.

Where.name: Where
Where.short_desc: Filters the values by a supplied predicate.

GroupBy.name: GroupBy
GroupBy.short_desc: Groups values according the supplied function.
GroupBy.long_desc:
(Uses strict equality '===')
The values will be grouped into instances of ITraversable.

AndBy.name: AndBy
AndBy.short_desc: Subsequently groups values according the supplied function.

Join.name: Join
Join.short_desc: Matches the original values with the supplied values according to the supplied function.

GroupJoin.name: GroupJoin
GroupJoin.short_desc: Matches the original values with the supplied values according to the supplied functions then groups the values.

Union.name: Union
Union.short_desc: Returns unique results present in both the original and supplied values,  keys will be reindexed.

Intersect.name: Intersect
Intersect.short_desc: Returns unique values the are present in the original and supplied values.

Difference.name: Difference
Difference.short_desc: Removes unique values from the original not present in the supplied values.

Append.name: Append
Append.short_desc: Returns values from the original and supplied values, keys will be reindexed.

WhereIn.name: WhereIn
WhereIn.short_desc: Returns all values from the original present in the supplied values.

Except.name: Except
Except.short_desc: Returns values all values from the original not present in the supplied values.

Skip.name: Skip
Skip.short_desc: Skip the amount of values from the start.

Amount.name: Amount
Amount.short_desc: The amount of values to skip, must be > 0

Take.name: Take
Take.short_desc: Limits the amount of values by the supplied amount

Amount.name: Amount
Amount.short_desc: The amount of values to retrieve, must be > 0 or null if all

Slice.name: Slice
Slice.short_desc: Retrieve a slice of the values

Start.name: Start
Start.short_desc: The amount of values to skip

Amount.name: Amount
Amount.short_desc: The amount of values to retrieve

OrderByAscending.name: OrderByAscending
OrderByAscending.short_desc: Orders the values mapped from the supplied function ascendingly

OrderByDescending.name: OrderByDescending
OrderByDescending.short_desc: Orders the values mapped from the supplied function descendingly

ThenBy.name: ThenBy
ThenBy.short_desc: Subsequently orders the results using the supplied function according to the supplied direction

ThenByAscending.name: ThenByAscending
ThenByAscending.short_desc: Subsequently orders the results using the supplied function ascendingly

ThenByDescending.name: ThenByDescending
ThenByDescending.short_desc: Subsequently orders the results using the supplied function descendingly

OrderBy.name: OrderBy
OrderBy.short_desc: Orders the values mapped from the supplied function according the supplied direction.

First.name: First
First.short_desc: Returns the first value, null if empty

Last.name: Last
Last.short_desc: Returns the last value, null if empty

Count.name: Count
Count.short_desc: Returns the amount of the values.

Contains.name: Contains
Contains.short_desc: Returns whether the supplied value is contained within the aggregate

Aggregate.name: Aggregate
Aggregate.short_desc: Aggregates the values with the supplied function

All.name: All
All.short_desc: Returns a boolean of if all the values evaluate to true

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Any.name: Any
Any.short_desc: Returns a boolean of if any of the values evaluate to true

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Sum.name: Sum
Sum.short_desc: Returns the sum of the values.

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Average.name: Average
Average.short_desc: Returns the average of the values.

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values

Implode.name: Implode
Implode.short_desc: Returns a string of all the values concatented by the delimiter

Delimiter.name: Delimiter
Delimiter.short_desc: The string to delimit the values by

Function.name: Function
Function.short_desc: The function which will return the values
